eports a covered source line for the exact frame, so this kind of line-less generated helper may remain reported as uncovered even when the helper executes at runtime. No reachability metadata was edited.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c7ca982c283d368016a27f30755b48195bf6867feee638f60\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 874, "output": 1590, "cacheRead": 71680, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 74144, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781002973823, "responseId": "resp_0c7ca982c283d368016a27f2de6d608195b9c9ff06cb50214a"}, "toolResults": []}
